entries.s_10: To get off of Dathomir...there isn't a problem with my ticket, right? How about the ship...is it coming?
entries.s_11: I'm sure everything is fine trooper. Why are you out of uniform?
entries.s_13: Uniform? Oh, that. They tore it off...well some pieces I pulled off so I could run away faster.
entries.s_17: The...things. The virus changed everyone when it was released. All my friends...they change. They chased me.
entries.s_32: I'm a soldier right? I should be able to handle this. I just want to go home to Gala.
entries.s_5: Is there a problem with my ticket?
